{"tid":1545282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9月14 天水圍親子大遊行正式上線了！","createTime":"2019-09-06T00:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T02:32:31.000Z","uid":6630,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f04d282d68d5123a6afef3161de235c49ba4db46","tid":1545282,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:53:51.000Z","msg":"<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">代post</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8abvQ0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8abvQ0s.jpg&h=96923c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVksTdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVksTdO.jpg&h=f47cd468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反送中活動至今已經踏入第三個月。<br />\n當中有手足以死明志，步上絕路的手足近半數表示除了社會現況，家庭關係亦令他們感到無力⋯⋯<br />\n天水圍過往被標籤為「悲情城市」，連日來街坊團結表達訴求，曾經的悲情城市，其實比想像中更有愛。<br />\n<br />\n天水圍居民接收反修例運動資訊處於被動狀況，亦較少直接接觸運動的機會，故此希望居民能透過活動有新體會，同時增加居民對五大訴求同示威者的認知，減低偏見。<br />\n<br />\n親子遊主題以「溝通」為主軸，提供一個機會讓家長嘗試了解年輕一代的心聲，了解年輕一代擔憂香港未來以及警察濫權以及無差別恐襲等問題。是次活動亦希望街坊藉此多角度了解五大訴求，及年輕抗爭者堅持上街爭取的因由。<br />\n<br />\n是次活動歡迎任何年齡層朋友參與，據以往社區活動經驗，預料會有不少孩童參與，主辦方將以和平理性為大原則舉辦活動。<br />\n <br />\n公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/BVNW9FVRfcdydEOs-pbBTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FBVNW9FVRfcdydEOs-pbBTg&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=98421e8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/BVNW9FVRfcdydEOs-pbBTg</a>"},{"pid":"d92f40eb31fe77a9c6a99600c6bb478e8a072f78","tid":1545282,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:57:18.000Z","msg":"支持，過完中秋就可以去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b66b08afed41d40bebec06e4b3871f3fde2b93","tid":1545282,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3798df7d56287